        "description": {
            "value": "<p>These sturdy leather sandals feature straps that wrap up to the knees. Etched in the leather are intricate patterns of stags leaping through the forest. You gain a +5-foot item bonus to your land Speed and a +3 item bonus on Athletics checks when attempting to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.High Jump] or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Long Jump]. When you invest the sandals, you either increase your Strength score by 2 or increase it to 18, whichever is higher.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">R</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per minute</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You attempt a High Jump or Long Jump but you didn't Stride at least 10 feet</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You can attempt the jump normally. It doesn't automatically fail.</p>"
